description.en:
What is the project about?

meme coin
What makes your project unique?
The attitude of the project party and the activeness of the community are very high

History of your project.
There is a famous TV series in China called Hurricane, one of the characters in it is FengLvZi, he is very clever and cunning, and he is very popular because of his naughty style

What’s next for your project?
Increase the market value, increase the number of addresses, ecological construction and CEX listing plan

What can your token be used for?

At present, it can only be used for buying and selling, and the pledge function will be launched soon
